description:
Dictionary with results of experiments aaa(g, h, i, j, k, l ,m, n) (104 models trained). 
 Keys: 
 -> val_recursive_1hour_models_15epochs: recursive 1hr validation for all models trained 15 epochs. 
 -> val_epoch_loss: val loss for each epoch for each model 
 -> disc_epoch_loss: disc loss for each epoch for each model 
 -> gen_epoch_loss: gen loss for each epoch for each model 
 -> best_val_loss_and_epoch: best val_loss recursive 1hr and epoch in which happens.
